{"word":"H8068 - שָׁמִיר - shâmîyr - shaw-meer' - Adamant","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁמִיר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâmîyr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-meer'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Adamant"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"முட்செடி, வைரம், வச்சிரக்கல் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"thorn(s), adamant, flint, a diamond"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H8104 - שָׁמַר - shâmar - shaw-mar'/8104\">H8104</a> in the original sense of <i>pricking</i>; a <i>thorn</i>; also (from its <i>keenness</i> for scratching) a gem, probably the <i>diamond: - </i>adamant (stone), brier, diamond."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8053 - שָׁמוּר - Shâmûwr - shaw-moor'/8053\">H8053</a>, <a href=\"#/H8068 - שָׁמִיר - shâmîyr - shaw-meer'/8068\">H8068</a>, <a href=\"#/H8069 - שָׁמִיר - Shâmîyr - shaw-meer'/8069\">H8069</a>"}]}